The evidence with the title 'Strategic Petroleum Reserve fast facts - CNN ' says Jan 18, 2017  ... January 16 , 1991 - president George H.W. Bush orders the first emergency drawdown of the SPR. September 2000 - president Bill Clinton releases 30 million barrels of oil in the SPR, to increase home heating oil supplies and lower gasoline prices which had risen to more than $2 a gallon in some areas. 
